 <description translatable="no">

<p>EcotubeHQ is an easy to use video player based on mpv which utilizes a unique buffering method to minimize data retrieved from streaming services such as YouTube. It is compatible with the X Window System and Wayland display server and is hardware accelerated. It employs two fullscreen output methods - 'Quality' and 'Powersave' - 'Quality' optimizes video quality via AMD FidelityFX Super Resolution, and 'Powersave' minimizes CPU usage through fast video upscaling.</p>
      <p>Features:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ offers auto codec selection and hardware acceleration on av1, vp9, h.264 and h.265 videos.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ automatically plays 144p / 240p YouTube videos in a miniplayer.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ automatically updates yt-dlp and FFmpeg to optimize player performance and minimize playback issues.</li>
      </ul>
 </description>
